    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Recognizes Liu Xiaobo for his decades of peaceful struggle for basic human rights and democracy in the People's Republic of China.</p> <p>Urges the Chinese government to unconditionally release Liu Xiaobo and his wife, Liu Xia, and the President to seek their humanitarian transfer from China so that Liu Xiaobo can seek medical treatment in the United States or elsewhere overseas.</p><ul> </ul>]]></text>
